  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I know it&rsquo;s a silly name. See, I found a <a href="http://doctorwhoscarf.com">pattern site</a> for scarves from the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doctor_Who">Doctor Who</a> TV show. <a href="http://doctorwhoscarf.com">http://doctorwhoscarf.com</a> contains great patterns and solid advice throughout. This scarf uses the pattern for the <a href="http://www.doctorwhoscarf.com/s12.html">original scarf</a>, with some differences.</p>
<p><img src="/post/2015/11/../../../attachments/img/2015/cover-2015-11-02.jpg" alt="attachments/img/2015/cover-2015-11-02.jpg"/></p>
<ul>
<li>I replaced the original scarf colors with an assortment of greens.</li>
